fields.name: Natures Aid
fields.description: Multivitamins & Minerals without Iron has been carefully formulated by our expert nutritionists to provide a handy daily top-up of key nutrients, the ideal choice for those who would prefer a multivitamin without iron. Our vegan-friendly, One-A-Day tablets are a unique combination of 21 active ingredients and provide your body with the daily requirement of many essential vitamins and minerals.

fields.name: Holland & Barrett High Strength Super Multi Mineral 90 Tablets
fields.description: Holland & Barrett Super MultiMineral tablets feature a unique formulation of major and trace minerals for those individuals who may not receive enough through diet alone. This multimineral formula includes: Calcium - contributes to the maintenance of normal bones and muscle function. Chromium - helps to maintain normal blood glucose levels. Copper - contributes to the normal function of the immune system & normal iron transport in the body. Iodine - contributes to normal thyroid function and the production of thyroid hormones. Iron - contributes to the reduction of tiredness and to normal energy yielding metabolism. Magnesium - contributes to the maintenance of normal bones & teeth, and the reduction of tiredness & fatigue. Manganese - contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress, supports bone health & contributes to the normal formation of connective tissue. Selenium - helps with the maintenance of normal hair & nails. Zinc - contributes to the normal function of a healthy immune system, and the maintenance of strong and healthy skin, hair and nails.

fields.name: BioCare Mineral Complex (30cps)
fields.description: Mineral Complex provides a comprehensive combination of essential minerals including magnesium, zinc, selenium & chromium for energy, immune & skin support.

fields.name: Multivitamins and Minerals - 365 Vegetarian Multivitamin Tablets - 27g
fields.description: 27 ESSENTIAL VITAMINS AND MINERALS PER TABLET - Each micro multivitamin tablet delivers AtoZ vitamins and minerals - Vitamin A, Vitamin D, Vitamin E, Vitamin K, Vitamin C, Vitamin B Complex including all 8 Vitamin B (Thiamin, Riboflavin, Niacin, Vitamin B6, Folic Acid, Vitamin B12, Biotin, Pantothenic Acid), Calcium, Magnesium, Zinc, Iron, Copper, Iodine, Manganese, Sodium, Potassium, Selenium, Chromium, Molybdenum, Potassium Chloride, Sodium Chloride and Dicalcium Phosphate.ONE A DAY MULTIVITAMINS & MINERALS - Formulated to support both men and women providing 100% of your recommended daily intake of Vitamin D3, Vitamin E, Vitamin B Complex, Copper, Iodine, Selenium and Zinc and more.

fields.name: Solgar Calcium, Magnesium & Zinc 100 Tablets
fields.description: We know calcium keeps our bones and teeth strong and healthy.* But did you know magnesium and zinc are also essential to the maintenance of healthy bones and teeth?
